
* Additional, package specific ./configure arguments:

--enable-init-as-parent

	enable treating init as possible parent of sessions default=no

--enable-need-root

	enable program to work only if run by superuser default=no
    
--with-utmp-file path to UTMP file

	in most common cases /var/run/utmpx, but may use /var/run/utmp on some systems
	note that /var/run/utmp or whatever found in <paths.h> will be checked additionaly,
	even if not specified here

